    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
私しが土佐に帰りたりときくと、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">幕吏</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゑどやく</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>が大<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">恐</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おそ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れぞ、はやきおもみ申候。四方の浪人らがたずねてきて、どふもおかしい。近日京ニ後藤庄次郎どのおらんと思ひ候。其時ハ伏見の寺田やでやどかり、伏見奉行をおそれさしてやろふとぞんじおり候。<lb />
何かさしあげ度候得ども、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鳥渡</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（ちよつと）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>これなく白<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">がね</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（金巾）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">き</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（ママ）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">ひとき</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（一匹）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>さしあげ候。<lb />
御めしものニ被<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>成候得バ、ありがたし。かしく。<lb />
<span rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">四月七日<span rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">龍馬</span></span>
<span rend="jisage_3" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 3em">乙様</span>
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
